Which Qiskit fragment implements the same operations and classical-bit mapping as this OpenQASM 3 program?

```qasm
OPENQASM 3.0;
include "stdgates.inc";
bit[3] c;
qubit[3] q;
h q[1];
cx q[1], q[2];
c[2] = measure q[1];
c[0] = measure q[2];
```

